items.name: State-Infrastructure-Progress-Report
items.description: Road Construction Analysis (PMGSY) — A data-driven project to analyze and visualize the progress of rural road construction in India under the Pradhan Mantri Gram Sadak Yojana (PMGSY). This includes calculating average road lengths, road completion rates per state, and visualizing the distribution of sanctioned projects using pivot tables, charts.
